1
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:29,400
Zhinian,

2
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:30,760
come in.

3
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,720
Come in.

4
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,160
Linglong,

5
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:42,800
you're awake.

6
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,320
Zhinian,

7
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:48,500
take a seat.

8
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,360
Zhinian,

9
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:02,200
you saved me again.

10
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:06,080
I don't know how to repay you.

11
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:09,199
Since you can't repay him,

12
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,560
why not just marry him?

13
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:11,880
Anyway, the two of you

14
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:13,400
already have feelings for each other.

15
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:15,530
You just haven't made it official yet.

16
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:16,640
Linglong,

17
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:20,160
there's no need to thank me for saving you.

18
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:20,840
But...

19
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:31,360
By the way,

20
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,220
near the teahouse that night,

21
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,329
did you notice anyone suspicious?

22
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,880
More than suspicious.

23
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,440
It's concrete evidence.

24
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,800
When that man attacked,

25
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,200
I saw him with my own eyes.

26
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,840
He was around 40 years old.

27
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,440
As for his build,

28
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,120
he was a head taller than you.

29
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:49,079
He had small eyes and a narrow nose bridge.

30
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:50,200
On his left cheek,

31
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:51,240
there was a scar.

32
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,960
The man had very dark skin.

33
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:55,040
He must have knocked you out with knockout gas first,

34
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:56,720
then poured tung oil all over the room,

35
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:57,640
and planned to kidnap you.

36
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:59,160
If I hadn't accidentally knocked over the oil lamp,

37
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,040
he would have succeeded.

38
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:01,770
There was indeed such a person.

39
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:04,840
He looked to be around 40.

40
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,530
A bit taller than me.

41
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,800
Dark skin and small eyes.

42
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,600
And a distinct scar on his face.

43
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:15,250
He didn't want to kill me to silence me;

44
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,060
he just wanted to take me away.

45
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,640
But when the teahouse caught fire,

46
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:19,600
he ran away.

47
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:27,040
Linglong,

48
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:27,890
don't worry.

49
00:03:28,079 --> 00:03:28,880
Now that we know what he looks like,

50
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:30,410
we can definitely find him.

51
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:32,560
It's only a matter of time before we find him.

52
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,480
We must report this to the authorities.

53
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:35,079
Linglong,

54
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,360
I will help you look for him.

55
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,480
The person who hurt you,

56
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,740
I will never let him go.

57
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,050
By the way, Zhinian,

58
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,730
I haven't asked you yet.

59
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,760
The teahouse caught fire at night.

60
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,520
Why were you there?

61
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:00,640
Linglong,

62
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,120
you shouldn't overthink right now.

63
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,320
It's a long story.

64
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:06,080
I'll tell you about it later.

65
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:07,000
Okay.

66
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:16,680
I...

67
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,240
Let me feed you the medicine.

68
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,370
Linglong...

69
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:35,240
I...

70
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:35,760
I'm sorry.

71
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:36,320
I...

72
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:38,640
It's my first time feeding someone medicine.

73
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:39,570
I'm a bit clumsy.

74
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:40,080
I'm...

75
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:40,720
sorry.

76
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,130
You're both adults.

77
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:50,540
Watching you two date is so frustrating.

78
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,460
You're grown-ups.

79
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:59,700
Yet you're so shy just holding hands.

80
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:12,520
Hey.

81
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,800
That's right.

82
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:30,560
Aunt.

83
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,360
Mother.

84
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:39,800
Aunt.

85
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:40,600
I...

86
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,860
I'll take my leave.

87
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:43,520
Zhinian.

88
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:47,200
I'll walk you out.

89
00:05:59,159 --> 00:06:00,000
Zhinian.

90
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:04,280
Aunt.

91
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:06,640
I can tell you have something to say.

92
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,970
Please speak your mind.

93
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:11,680
Zhinian.

94
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:13,160
You saved Linglong.

95
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:14,840
I am very grateful to you.

96
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,920
I also know

97
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,640
you two grew up together

98
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,000
and are very close.

99
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:21,960
But...

100
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:25,560
But Linglong's current status is special.

101
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:27,840
And she made a vow in the ancestral hall.

102
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,760
You can be friends,

103
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,000
but you cannot overstep the bounds.

104
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:33,880
You know your limits,

105
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,600
don't you?

106
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:37,680
Aunt,

107
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,600
I understand.

108
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,460
I'll take my leave.

109
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:59,200
Didn't you say that if I left this to you,

110
00:06:59,200 --> 00:07:00,460
it would be foolproof?

111
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:02,040
Now Hu Linglong is not dead,

112
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,780
and the arsonist has escaped.

113
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,780
If Hu Linglong finds the witness,

114
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,000
what should we do?

115
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:07,960
Father,

116
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,360
it's not my fault.

117
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:11,840
That old teahouse is unvisited all year round.

118
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,160
I didn't expect that in the middle of the night,

119
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:15,200
Xu Zhinian would appear there.

120
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,920
Xu Zhinian.

121
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,320
Xu Zhinian again.

122
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:20,240
Yes.

123
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,360
Mr. Yamamoto.

124
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,920
Since that day in the ancestral hall,

125
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:23,800
I began to suspect.

126
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,400
Hu Linglong and Xu Zhinian,

127
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:26,520
in the middle of the night,

128
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:27,640
must have been doing some

129
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:28,960
shameful deeds.

130
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,840
The most urgent task

131
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:33,800
is to find the arsonist

132
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,880
and silence him.

133
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:37,560
Yes.

134
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:39,560
Is there any information about him,

135
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:40,880
Mr. Yamamoto?

136
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,770
The man is called Wang Song,

137
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,640
the bandit leader of Qingfeng Stronghold.

138
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:46,840
He has done a lot of things for us before.

139
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:49,320
Since he failed that day,

140
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:49,720
he just

141
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,159
disappeared.

142
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,440
He's very cunning.

143
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,320
He probably knows

144
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,400
we won't let him go,

145
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,120
so he

146
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:55,440
hid

147
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,320
hid away.

148
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:59,250
He knows this matter is related to me and your father.

149
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,970
We must not leave him alive,

150
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,960
otherwise there will be endless trouble.

151
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:03,690
Understood.

152
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,640
What are you waiting for?

153
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,280
Go now.

154
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,320
If you mess this up again,

155
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,920
I will no longer consider you my son.

156
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:12,360
Yes.

157
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,000
Get out.

158
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:13,760
Yes.

159
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,480
You

160
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,640
are from the Hu family,

161
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,700
here to silence me,

162
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,320
right?

163
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,520
You are not from the Hu family.

164
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:32,440
Who are you?

165
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:34,200
Who I am is not important.

166
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,700
Just answer what I ask.

167
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,480
Do you hear me?

168
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,520
Spare my life!

169
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,250
That night at the teahouse,

170
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,440
why did you take Hu Linglong away?

171
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,240
What's the grudge between you two?

172
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:43,840
I...

173
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,970
I don't understand.

174
00:08:46,160 --> 00:08:47,760
I know a lot of things.

175
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:49,120
Don't even try to lie to me.

176
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,920
If I find out you're lying even a bit,

177
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:52,440
I'll take your pathetic life.

178
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,680
Understood.

179
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:56,040
I have no grudge against Hu Linglong.

180
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:56,920
It's...

181
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:59,080
Someone else wants her dead.

182
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:00,200
Who?

183
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,840
Hu Wenyi of the Hu family,

184
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:02,800
and that

185
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,800
Japanese guy named Yamamoto Toru.

186
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:07,640
What exactly do they want?

187
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:08,320
I...

188
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,480
I don't know.

189
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:10,840
I only know that

190
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,240
Hu Wenyi has always

191
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:15,240
wanted to kill Hu Wenzhong's entire family.

192
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:17,040
He poisoned Hu Wenzhong.

193
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:19,000
Next in line is naturally

194
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,120
his daughter.

195
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:21,960
Who?

196
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,760
Who poisoned him?

197
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,600
Hu Wenyi of the Hu family.

198
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:48,680
Long'er.

199
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,400
Why aren't you resting?

200
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:51,480
Why are you up?

201
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,160
Mother,

202
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,840
I've been in bed for more than three days.

203
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,120
I'm fully recovered now.

204
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,040
As for the medicine,

205
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:58,500
you don't need to bother brewing it anymore.

206
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:08,200
I can't let your efforts go to waste.

207
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:08,880
Today,

208
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:10,080
this is the last bowl.

209
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:11,200
Uncle Zhao said

210
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:13,520
a lot of work has piled up these past few days.

211
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:15,450
I have to go deal with it right away.

212
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:16,800
Sigh.

213
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,920
This child...

214
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:23,650
How come she is different from before?

215
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:38,960
Linglong.

216
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:42,760
Zhinian.

217
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:58,480
Linglong.

218
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:00,450
I am about to take up my new post.

219
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:02,160
The future of this journey is uncertain.

220
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:04,090
I don't know when we'll meet again.

221
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,580
Before I leave,

222
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:08,450
let's make some more beautiful memories.

223
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,160
Let me do it myself.

224
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:03,280
Look.

225
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,400
Zhinian.

226
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:21,640
Do you...

227
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:23,570
have anything you want to say to me?

228
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:48,520
Oh.

229
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:52,400
There is a small cabin over there.

230
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:53,930
Do you want to go take a look?

231
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:57,040
There's a man-eating monster in the cabin.

232
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:58,700
If you want to go, go yourself.

233
00:12:58,720 --> 00:13:00,080
There are no monsters in this world.

234
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:00,680
Linglong,

235
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:02,040
we'll know once we go.

236
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:03,320
Mm.

237
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:26,960
Zhinian.

238
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:28,520
I'm scared.

239
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,200
It's okay.

240
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:31,960
I'm here.

241
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:44,240
Ah!
